text: Nummah jahannam Jinnii kee Seehadak maggo marah ginne, usun cakki edde Aaxige waan lubbitte lon, Yallih inkittinaane kee kay dudda tascasse Astooti edde able waan intiita lon, Yallih Aayoota edde Aabbe waan aytiita lon, woo mari usun Lactinnah yan mara, wonna hinnay usun woo Lacak makot gexoh gacak Raaqan, woo mari usun iimaan kee Yallih taaqatak garcit yan mara kinni
